<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
   <head>
      <meta charset="UTF-8" />
      <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
      <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
      <title>OTP Verification - MOTOFILA</title>
      <style>
         body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
         }

         .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
         }

         .header {
            background-color: #35415B;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
         }

         .content {
            padding: 20px;
            color: #333;
         }

         .otp-code {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #070707;
         }

         .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            color: #777;
         }

         .footer a {
            color: #3498db;
            text-decoration: none;
         }
      </style>
   </head>
   <body>
      <div class="container">
         <div class="header">
            <h2 style="margin: 0">MOTOFILA - OTP Verification</h2>
         </div>
         <div class="content">
            <p>Hello <strong>MOTOFILA VENDOR</strong>,</p>
            <p>
               Thank you for Partner With MOTOFILA! Your OTP for account verification is:
               <span class="otp-code"><%= otp %></span>.
            </p>
            <p>Please use this OTP to complete the verification process on our website.</p>
            <p>If you did not request this OTP, please ignore this email.</p>
         </div>
         <div class="footer">
            <p>
               Best Regards,<br />
               MOTOFILA Team
            </p>
            <p>Need help? Contact our <a href="mailto:support@motofila.com">support team</a>.</p>
         </div>
      </div>
   </body>
</html>
